title: アオハル杯4戦目にむけて

text.jpText:
『アオハル杯』4戦目。ライスシャワーは
自分の不幸で迷惑をかけている分、少しでも
皆の力になればと応援の練習に励むのだった。
text.enText:
The fourth round of the "Aoharu Hai." Rice 
Shower was trying hard to practice cheering 
to help everyone as much as possible to make 
up for the inconvenience caused by her 
misfortune. She was practicing her cheering 
in the hope that she could help everyone.
